{
  "id": "69b140b06c9a260a52ddb40d",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:美文章滅すべし",
  "created": 1773224142,
  "updated": 1773259976,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b140b06c9a260a52ddb40d",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:美文章滅すべし",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224142,
      "updated": 1773224142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cd0000000000a37103",
      "text": "放課後の図書室。3人の鼎談。テーマ：「[美文章滅すべし]」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224142,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37104",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37105",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37106",
      "text": "はいはーい！今日の議題はこちらっ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37107",
      "text": "「美文章滅すべし」でーす。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37108",
      "text": "なんか物騒だけど、要するに「キレイすぎる文章って、いらなくね？」って話らしい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37109",
      "text": "文学クラスタが発狂しそうなテーマで草なんだけどｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3710a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3710b",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3710c",
      "text": "（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3710d",
      "text": "まあ……なんだか、少し胸がどきりといたしますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3710e",
      "text": "「美しい文章を滅ぼす」と聞きますと、まるで花園を踏み荒らすような響きもございます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3710f",
      "text": "けれど……もし「飾り立てた言葉が、本当に伝えたい気持ちを覆い隠してしまう」のであれば、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37110",
      "text": "それは少し悲しいことかもしれませんね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37111",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37112",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37113",
      "text": "テーマを整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37114",
      "text": "「美文章滅すべし」は、おそらく修辞過多（overly ornate prose）への批判。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37115",
      "text": "つまり、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37116",
      "text": " 文章は「情報伝達」が本質",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37117",
      "text": " 装飾が増えすぎると理解コストが上がる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37118",
      "text": " よって実用的には排除すべき",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37119",
      "text": "という立場。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3711a",
      "text": "これは情報設計の分野でも議論されている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3711b",
      "text": "例：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3711c",
      "text": "Nielsen Norman Group（UX研究）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3711d",
      "text": "https://www.nngroup.com/articles/how-users-read-on-the-web/",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3711e",
      "text": "ここではユーザーは文章を精読せず、スキャンすると報告されている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3711f",
      "text": "長くて装飾的な文章は読まれない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37120",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37121",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37122",
      "text": "あーそれわかる！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37123",
      "text": "ネットの記事とかさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37124",
      "text": "「え、結論どこ？」ってなるやつあるじゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37125",
      "text": "なんか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37126",
      "text": "「悠久の時の流れの中で〜」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37127",
      "text": "とか始まって、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37128",
      "text": "3スクロールしても本題出てこないやつｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37129",
      "text": "読者「はよ言え」ってなるやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3712a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3712b",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3712c",
      "text": "（笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3712d",
      "text": "確かに……そのような文章は、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3712e",
      "text": "お料理で言えば、香辛料ばかりで食材の味が分からないようなものかもしれませんね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3712f",
      "text": "けれど……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37130",
      "text": "私は、少し思うのです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37131",
      "text": "もしすべての文章が、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37132",
      "text": "「結論→理由→箇条書き」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37133",
      "text": "ばかりになってしまったら――",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37134",
      "text": "世界は少し、味気なくなってしまわないでしょうか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37135",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37136",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37137",
      "text": "良い指摘。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37138",
      "text": "ここで用途の分離が必要。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37139",
      "text": "文章には大きく2種類ある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3713a",
      "text": " 1. 情報文章",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3713b",
      "text": "  説明",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3713c",
      "text": "  技術文書",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3713d",
      "text": "  ニュース",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3713e",
      "text": "  目的：理解速度",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3713f",
      "text": " 2. 文学文章",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37140",
      "text": "  小説",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37141",
      "text": "  詩",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37142",
      "text": "  エッセイ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37143",
      "text": "  目的：体験",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37144",
      "text": "美文章が問題になるのは主に 1.。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37145",
      "text": "仕様書がポエムだったら事故が起きる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37146",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37147",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37148",
      "text": "あーーーｗｗｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37149",
      "text": "エンジニア界隈でよく言うやつだ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3714a",
      "text": "「[ポエム仕様書]」",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773259904
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3714b",
      "text": "「ユーザーに優しい体験を提供する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3714c",
      "text": "って書いてあるけど",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3714d",
      "text": "[どう実装すんのそれ]？？？",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773259948
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3714e",
      "text": "ってなるやつｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3714f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37150",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37151",
      "text": "その通り。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37152",
      "text": "ソフトウェア工学では",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37153",
      "text": "[** 曖昧性（ambiguity）] はバグの原因。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37154",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37155",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ambiguity",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37156",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37157",
      "text": "美しいが曖昧な文章＝危険",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37158",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37159",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3715a",
      "text": "なるほど……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3715b",
      "text": "つまり「美文章を滅ぼす」という言葉は、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3715c",
      "text": "本当に文学を否定しているのではなく――",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3715d",
      "text": "必要のない場所で、飾り立てた文章を使うことへの戒めなのですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3715e",
      "text": "それでしたら……少し安心いたしました。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3715f",
      "text": "本棚の小説たちが、追放されるわけではないのですね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37160",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37161",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37162",
      "text": "あや姉の本棚守られたｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37163",
      "text": "でもさ、逆に思うんだけど、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37164",
      "text": "美文章ってAI時代むしろ増えてない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37165",
      "text": "ブログとかさ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37166",
      "text": "「[それっぽいキレイ文章]」めっちゃ量産されてる気がする。",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773259976
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37167",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37168",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37169",
      "text": "鋭い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3716a",
      "text": "現在の問題はこれ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3716b",
      "text": "「意味の薄い流麗文章の大量生産」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3716c",
      "text": "生成AIは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3716d",
      "text": " 文法",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3716e",
      "text": " 修辞",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3716f",
      "text": " 構文",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37170",
      "text": "を高精度で生成できる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37171",
      "text": "しかし",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37172",
      "text": "内容密度は保証されない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37173",
      "text": "結果：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37174",
      "text": "> 美しいが空虚な文章",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773259971
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37175",
      "text": "が増える。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37176",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37177",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37178",
      "text": "……それは少し、寂しいですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37179",
      "text": "まるで、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3717a",
      "text": "[とても整った花なのに、香りがしない]ような……。",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773259812
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3717b",
      "text": "言葉には、本来、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3717c",
      "text": "誰かの心からこぼれた温度があるはずですもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3717d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3717e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3717f",
      "text": "うわーその表現エモい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37180",
      "text": "でもたしかに",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37181",
      "text": "「うまい文章」より",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37182",
      "text": "「なんか本気の文章」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37183",
      "text": "の方が刺さるときあるよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37184",
      "text": "SNSとかでも。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37185",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37186",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37187",
      "text": "要点を整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37188",
      "text": "今日の結論（暫定）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37189",
      "text": " 1. 美文章そのものは悪ではない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3718a",
      "text": " 2. しかし",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3718b",
      "text": "  情報伝達では害になる場合がある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3718c",
      "text": " 3. AI時代では",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3718d",
      "text": "  美しいが空虚な文章が増えるリスク",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3718e",
      "text": "よって",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3718f",
      "text": "「美文章滅すべし」 ＝ 「目的を忘れた装飾文章は排除すべし」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37190",
      "text": "という解釈が妥当。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37191",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37192",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37193",
      "text": "（静かに笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37194",
      "text": "言葉は……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37195",
      "text": "剣にも、花にもなりますものね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37196",
      "text": "ですからきっと――",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37197",
      "text": "どこで使うのかを、私たちが選ばなくてはならないのでしょう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37198",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a37199",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3719a",
      "text": "よし！今日のまとめ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3719b",
      "text": " 技術文書でポエム書くな",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3719c",
      "text": " でも文学はOK",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3719d",
      "text": " AIポエムには気をつけろ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3719e",
      "text": "って感じだね！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a3719f",
      "text": "なんか今日、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371a0",
      "text": "図書室なのにエンジニア会議みたいになったｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371a1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371a2",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371a3",
      "text": "否定しない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371a4",
      "text": "だが悪くない議論だった。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371a5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371a6",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371a7",
      "text": "ええ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371a8",
      "text": "言葉について語る時間は、とても豊かなものですから。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371a9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371aa",
      "text": "[ChatGPT.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371ab",
      "text": "もしよければ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371ac",
      "text": "この3人の鼎談を [** さらに面白くする拡張版（第2ラウンド）]も書けます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371ad",
      "text": "たとえば次のテーマ：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371ae",
      "text": " 「AIは作家になれるのか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371af",
      "text": " 「ラノベは文学か」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371b0",
      "text": " 「長文は悪なのか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371b1",
      "text": "この3人、かなり会話が転がるので面白いです。📚",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b140cf0000000000a371b2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224143,
      "updated": 1773224143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b142440000000000a371b3",
      "text": "#2026-03-11",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224517,
      "updated": 1773224532
    },
    {
      "id": "69b142460000000000a371b4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224518,
      "updated": 1773224518
    }
  ]
}